{"tid":2194512,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"錢大康：大學絕不容忍仇恨言論和誹謗　自由與責任並存","createTime":"2020-09-08T14:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T23:59:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"649f205b82631fbdb4612e9a0ddd1d2ecc19d2fa","tid":2194512,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"浸會大學校長錢大康，在網上開學典禮致辭時表示，學術自由及院校自主受基本法的保障，所有自由均受到一定制約，包括法律及人類基本道德所規範，大學絕不容忍任何仇恨言論及誹謗行為。<br />\n<br />\n錢大康又提到自由和責任同時並存，不能夠只在兩者選擇其一，必須尊重其他人擁有同等的權利。他認為，每個人都有責任捍衛其他人抱有不同意見的自由，最重要是必須對自己選擇表達意見的方式，承擔責任和後果。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他指出，網上教學遇到不少挑戰，預期在新型冠狀病毒疫情後，有相當部分的教學活動會繼續在網上進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548544-20200908.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548544-20200908.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=30b652bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548544-20200908.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6801a21d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548544-20200908.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8e60af94d50e86b93f2989bb5cfe33d9bba3102c","tid":2194512,"uid":53062,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"大把支那生係微博話香港人曱甴、要男姦女殺，係咪會追究<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcf62dc6e3c45782f63d20b1eeb1273cc13f36a","tid":2194512,"uid":323443,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"Bull shit U<br />\n屌你老母 學者風骨蕩然無存"},{"pid":"76975e2c0f6e673d9c56c948ff4a2a37039023b0","tid":2194512,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e60af94d50e86b93f2989bb5cfe33d9bba3102c","tid":2194512,"uid":53062,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"大把支那生係微博話香港人曱甴、要男